Package: montgomerycountymd
Title: Montgomery County, MD Open Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for Montgomery County, MD Socrata Open Data portal.
    Provides discovery, search, and data access for crime, arrests, crashes,
    permits, housing violations, and 422+ county datasets.
